https://www.ibm.com/docs/en/db2/11.5?topic=installing-verify-currently-installed-db2-version
Verify the currently installed Db2 version
c:\program Files\ibm\sqllib\bin>db2level

----begin
DB21085I  This instance or install (instance name, where applicable: "DB10")
uses "64" bits and DB2 code release "SQL11054" with level identifier "0605010F".
Informational tokens are "DB2 v11.5.4.0", "s2006161200", "DYN2006161200AMD64",
and Fix Pack "0".
Product is installed at "/opt/ibm/db2/V11.5".
----end
above command can show current instance : default is DB2,  this sample is DB10
  
c:\program Files\ibm\sqllib\bin>db2licm -l 
-----begin
Product name:                            "Db2 Advanced Edition"
License type:                            "Virtual Processor Core"
Expiry date:                             "Permanent"
Product identifier:                      "db2adv"
Version information:                     "11.5"
Enforcement policy:                      "Hard Stop"
Features:
IBM Db2 Performance Management Offering: "Not Licensed"
-----end
